<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Form Peminjaman Buku</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<style>
    body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f4f4f9;
        color: #333;
    }

    .header {
        background-color: #d7b5a8;
        color: white;
        padding: 15px 30px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .header .logo {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: bold;
    }

    .navbar a {
        color: white;
        font-size: 1rem;
        font-weight: bold;
        transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .navbar a:hover {
        color: #ffd7b5;
    }

    .container {
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 10px;
        padding: 70px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease;
    }

    .title {
        font-size: 1.8rem;
        color: #d7b5a8;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
    }

    .content {
        gap: 50px;
        margin-top: 50px;
    }

    .note h2 {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        color: #d7b5a8;
        font-weight: bold;
    }

    .note p {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: #d7b5a8;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .form-container {
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 15px;
        gap: 15px;
        padding: 25px;
        box-shadow: 0 6px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    }

    .form-container:hover {
        transform: scale(1.02);
        box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }

    .form-container input {
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
        padding: 12px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        transition: border-color 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    }

    .form-container input:focus {
        border-color: #d7b5a8;
        box-shadow: 0 0 6px rgba(215, 181, 168, 0.6);
        outline: none;
    }

    .btn {
        background-color: #d7b5a8;
        color: white;
        border: none;
        padding: 10px 15px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-weight: bold;
        font-size: 1rem;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
    }

    .btn:hover {
        background-color: #c59b8e;
        transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    footer {
        text-align: center;
        background-color: transparent;
        color: black;
        padding: 10px 0;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    /* Animasi untuk kontainer utama */
    @keyframes fadeIn {
        from {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(10px);
        }

        to {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }
    }
</style>

<body>
    <header class="header">
        <div class="logo">LOGO</div>
        <nav class="navbar">
            <a href="<%= url %>login">Logout</a>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main class="container">
        <h1 class="title">Form Peminjaman Buku</h1> <br>
        <h2>Caranya?</h2><br>
        <p> <br>
            Untuk meminjam buku, silakan isi formulir peminjaman yang tersedia di halaman ini. Pastikan Anda mengisi
            semua kolom yang diperlukan dengan informasi yang akurat, kemudian klik tombol "OK" untuk menyelesaikan
            proses peminjaman. Buku yang Anda pilih akan segera diproses.
        </p>
        <div class="content">
            <div class="note">
            </div>
            <div class="form-container">
                <form action="/peminjaman/save" method="POST">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="judul_buku">Judul Buku :</label>
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" name="judul_buku" id="judul_buku" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="tgl_pinjam">Tanggal Pinjam :</label>
                        <input type="date" class="form-control" name="tgl_pinjam" id="tgl_pinjam" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="tgl_kembali">Tanggal Kembali :</label>
                        <input type="date" class="form-control" name="tgl_kembali" id="tgl_kembali" required>
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Kirim</button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="footer">
        Â© 2024 Project Kelompok 3
    </footer>
</body>

</html>